questions.quote: John Germaine? That is amazing. I was just talking about him upstairs with Elaine.
Wait a second, I know what's happening. The no sex thing is having a reverse effect on you.
Whoa! Walking around naked? Ahh... that is not a good look for a man.
Have you seen his act? He's got a twelve-minute bit about Ovaltine. He's a punk, a patsy, a hack.
All right. I am happy, and I'll tell ya why -- because the two of you were making me and every one of your friends sick! Right, Elaine?
Well, they get very hot in the polyester. You know, it's not a natural fibre. I think they would prefer cotton.
It won't for a while. At least not until after the cast comes off.
I don't want to have anything to do with you or your perverted friends.  Ooohh, get away from me! You're horrible.
Jerry, get menus so when we sit down we can order right away.
You leave me no choice! You're the media now as far as I'm concerned!
